cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "Multiverse Signal Lab"
abstract: >
  A reproducible pipeline for searching exotic early-universe signatures
  (bubble collisions, cosmic strings) in CMB temperature and polarization maps.
  Includes matched-filter detection, Bayesian evidence computation, injection-recovery
  validation, and a digital twin CMB simulator.
version: "0.4.0"
date-released: "2025-01-01"
license: MIT
keywords:
  - CMB
  - cosmology
  - bubble collision
  - cosmic string
  - matched filter
  - injection recovery
  - reproducible science
  - digital twin
authors:
  - name: "Multiverse Signal Lab Contributors"
repository-code: "https://github.com/yourusername/multiverse-signal-lab"
